# Deploy and ports

- This project uses the **dev → production** workflow: develop locally, push with `npm run deploy` to 10.10.10.64.
- Production ports: **Frontend 3010**, **Backend 5010** (recorded in ~/.cursor/production-ports.md). New projects use 3020/5020, then +10.
- PM2 app names: `cybersecurity-backend`, `cybersecurity-frontend`. For other projects on the same server, use the **deploy-dev-to-production** skill and the ports registry.

## UFW on cod-node (10.10.10.64)

Run `scripts/setup-ufw-cod-node.sh` on the server to restrict access:
- SSH allowed only from 10.10.10.5 (run while connected from there to avoid lockout)
- Port 5010 allowed only from NPM (10.10.10.61)
- IPv6 disabled
